items.title: LIVE: Jail where United Healthcare CEO murder suspect is being held
items.author: Reuters
items.content:
Exterior of jail where Luigi Mangione, the suspect in case of murdered United Healthcare CEO Brian Thompson, is being held.

New York prosecutors filed a murder charge against Mangione in the killing of Thompson, a brazen shooting that set off a manhunt that culminated in his capture in Pennsylvania.

The action brought an end to a tense five-day manhunt for the suspected killer.
